{"tid":304688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大批古惑仔聚集銅鑼灣 聽候指示行動","createTime":"2017-07-01T05:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T06:34:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eac6a96a274b8198605e8c5c980b17614c259cf5","tid":304688,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:44:45.000Z","msg":"香港回歸二十年，國家主席習近平來港訪問，黑社會亦空群而出。 <br />\n<br />\n有反黑探員向《壹週刊》透露，本地多個社團，這幾天都派人出動，跟蹤一些主張港獨和反政府人士。而今天多個旺點街頭，都有大批古惑仔聚集，聽候指示行動。 <br />\n<br />\n而在銅鑼灣一酒店門外，下午六時許，亦聚集了大批古惑仔，其後有數名軍裝警員上前截查他們。 <br />\n<br />\n社民連黃浩銘表示，社民連長沙灣永明街的總部地下，長期有疑似黑社會人物駐守，有人自稱是14k，他們大概有8至10人。 <br />\n<br />\n回歸前夕，氣氛開始緊張起來。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170630/large/1498820655_578a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170630%2Flarge%2F1498820655_578a.jpg&h=eaff9e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"355d942699640e24e753ea7ffca576b18eb50ce4","tid":304688,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"c531fca9e66b9cad955efd7e6ddb758d866def0e","tid":304688,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"呢幾日見到幾千隻著藍衫既黑社會"},{"pid":"d0b12dd6b00ba12e31b1337fa2119a5158ab0fd3","tid":304688,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:57:06.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"0d2f4b8fac87dc7a222174a222c0c475a15d9355","tid":304688,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:04:32.000Z","msg":"警察知唔知醜?"},{"pid":"d53be033b0e48935472a48dad080bc9356c142bc","tid":304688,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"搵唔到班人"},{"pid":"bf29a8ab6a6de8aad97e470898e0a789578136d4","tid":304688,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵唔到班人</blockquote><br />\n早兩日架單新聞"}]}